quark.gui.config.subheader1: Quark's only got so much loot cause support o' %s%s%s and others.

quark.gui.config.bday: Get out ye rum, it's %s!'s birthday!'

quark.gui.celebration.vns: Get out ye rum, it's Capt'n MCVinnyq n' Sully's birthday!
quark.gui.celebration.vazkii: Get out ye rum, it's Capt'n Vazkii's birthday!
quark.gui.celebration.wire: Get out ye rum, it's Capt'n Segal's birthday!
quark.gui.celebration.afd: NO! ME TREASURE! THEY BE ALL GON... Just kidding! It be April Fools!
quark.gui.celebration.hw: Carve ye pumpkins... it be Halloween!
quark.gui.celebration.xmas: Give ye hearties a present... it be Christmas!
quark.gui.celebration.iwd: Write home - it be International Women's Day!
quark.gui.celebration.wpld: Spare th' ship with the green n' red flags... it be Portuguese Language Day!
quark.gui.celebration.iyd: Write home - it be International Youth Day!
quark.gui.celebration.wwd: Pour ye parrot a drink - it be World Wildlife Day!
quark.gui.celebration.hrd: No prisoners today - it be human's right day!
quark.gui.celebration.ny: Get ye rum - whole new year o' piratin'!
quark.camera.greetings: Greetin' by %s from the seven seas!
quark.readout.not_ingame: Na be in th' seas yet
quark.misc.now_afk: Ye be AFS (Away from th' Steering Wheel).

quark.misc.night_has_passed0: Praise lady luck, the ship survived th' night - it be a new day fer piratin'!
quark.misc.night_has_passed1: Praise lady luck, the ship survived th' night - many new treasures today.
quark.misc.night_has_passed2: Praise lady luck, the ship survived th' night - yo ho ho, it's a pirate's life fer me!
quark.misc.night_has_passed3: Praise lady luck, the ship survived th' night - get ye ou' there, me crew - No prey, no pay!
quark.misc.night_has_passed4: Praise lady luck, the ship survived th' night - there be many ships to plunder today!
quark.misc.night_has_passed5: Praise lady luck, the ship survived th' night - polish ye hook n' put on ye eye patch!
quark.misc.night_has_passed6: Praise lady luck, the ship survived th' night - now work so it survives 'nother!
quark.misc.night_has_passed7: Praise lady luck, the ship survived th' night - open ye sail n' swim on!
quark.misc.night_has_passed8: Praise lady luck, the ship survived th' night - go do some piratin'... capt'n's orders!
quark.misc.night_has_passed9: Praise lady luck, the ship survived th' night - avast, make ye day be worth!

quark.misc.map_shift: Tap shift to see ye sea

quark.misc.celebration: Drink to 10 years of Vazkii's Mods, me hearties!
